{"tid":120252,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友應該失戀","createTime":"2017-02-14T10:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T10:01:29.000Z","uid":34035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70ae77049dee3d6c0fd699b2fb483fa6a17929b8","tid":120252,"uid":34035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"今日見到某個朋友溝緊果條女拖住佢個兄弟。雖然最近冇來往，但都覺得佢幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能今晩條女就爆房同佢兄弟扑野，一路咬棍一路恥笑仲戇鳩鳩搞緊莊務嘅佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢唔係拍緊拖畀人戴緣帽已經算慶幸。<br />\n<br />\n唔止出到社會，喺大學已經唔撚會識到真朋友，襟兄弟就有份。<br />\n從來都係你當佢兄弟，佢當你契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時點撚樣friend底都好，喺女人面前根本不値一文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔排除會有例外，但遇唔到同冇有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0394dfde3fc48ff8526055c1ac9a846a406000","tid":120252,"uid":34035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"利申 我的朋友不是我<br />\n雖然我都係過來人"}]}